async fn test_cancellation_e2e_with_real_connector() {
    // End-to-end cancellation with actual connector
}

#[tokio::test]
async fn test_cancellation_under_load() {
    // Cancellation works correctly under high load
}
```

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] All unit tests pass
- [ ] Cancellation propagates within 100ms
- [ ] Cleanup runs correctly
- [ ] Partial results are available
- [ ] Checkpoint/resume works
- [ ] Audit trail is complete
- [ ] No memory leaks with many cancellations
